## 6. Campaign Type Naming Convention

Always refer to campaign types using their standard labels:

| Label | Type | Key Characteristics |
|---|---|---|
| **Type A** | Points (Direct Award) | Bulk upload of points to participants |
| **Type B** | Points (Approval-based) | Hierarchical allocation with controls, distribution mechanism |
| **Type C** | Claims (Invoice-based) | SKU-wise or total invoice claims, multi-level approval, OCR |
| **Type D** | Data / Automated Incentive | API/SFTP integration, calculation engine, KPI setup, approval flow, target distribution |
| **Type F** | Referral | Referral code generation, referee tracking, conversion logic |
| **Type G** | Scan & Earn | QR/barcode scanning, validation matrix, BST/FST tables, SKU-linked codes |

