## 7. Open Questions & Tagging

- Use **@FirstName LastName** format in .docx user stories.
- Open questions should appear inline (within the relevant AC bullet) or at the end under Next Steps.
- Do not leave open questions untagged.
- **Note:** Legacy PPT-format stories (from the previous PM) used #FirstName format (e.g. #Ankush, #Chetana). When extracting patterns from those PPTs into new .docx stories, convert to @FirstName LastName format.

